USDT(dot)pica.description:
A stablecoin issued by Tether that is pegged 1:1 to the USD.

USDT, or Tether, is a widely used stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, designed to maintain a stable value and facilitate transactions. This specific version has been bridged through Picasso's implementation of IBC on Ethereum.

WHINE.description: Whinecoin is an experimental memecoin by the Sommelier Finance team.

FX.description:
The native staking token of the Function X

FX coin is the native token on the Function X ecosystem. It is currently utilized as a governance token as well as a gas token on f(x)Core and f(x)EVM. The subnets that are built on the Function X ecosystem can also choose to utilize FX as their gas token.

PUNDIX.description:

PUNDIX token is the native token that functions within the Pundi X ecosystem, including PundiX Chain and XPOS. PUNDIX has several core use cases, including:

NIBI.description:
The native token of Nibiru network

Nibiru hosts a variety of ecosystem partners in a wide variety of consumer sectors. From RWAs (Coded Estate) to DeFi (Constella, NOM) to Gaming (Blockchain Game Alliance, IntoTheVerse), Nibiru is advancing multiple emerging blockchain narratives that will onboard the next billion users.

SHITMOS.description:
The Cosmos Network's premier self-hatred memecoin.

Shitmos is a fair launched token deployed via the start.cooking liquidity bootstrapping protocol (LBP) on the Osmosis blockchain. It is powered by the Shitmos Economic Zone (SEZ), and it has been designed with the goal of uniting the Cosmos Network and interchain-at-large ecosystems by making crypto fun. The SEZ is a federation of nft collections on Stargaze that supports Shitmos by providing at least 2% of royalties towards open market purchases of Shitmos.
